  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Levilehto Apartments are self-catering apartments. </p>
<p>Take the fuss out of meal and upgrade to the optional pre-bookable half board at the Sirkantahti Hotel (150 metres away). Fuel up for the day at the buffet breakfast which includes a continental offering with additional hot options. Dinner is also served buffet style and includes a choice of dishes and a salad bar.</p>
<p><span>Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music.</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
