  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>These excellent value, chalet-style apartments enjoy a convenient central location and offer a high standard of well-equipped accommodation. The apartments are 4 minutes' walk (400 metres) to the ski lifts and just 1-2 minutes' walk (100 metres) to the supermarket and village centre.</span></p>
<h2><span>Fully equipped apartments </span></h2>
<p><span>These chalet-style apartments offer a cosy accommodation, fully equipped with everything you may need for a break in <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a>. Each apartment has an open plan living area with tv and fully equipped kitchen, and a private sauna - perfect for warming up in after a day of Arctic adventures. The apartments vary in style and size, so make a great option for couples, families and friends looking for self catered accommodation in Levi. There is also the option to upgrade to half board, take the fuss out of meal times and enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet and a varied buffet style dinner at the <a data-udi="umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf}" title="Sirkantahti Hotel">Sirkantahti Hotel</a>. </span></p>
<h2><span>Great location</span></h2>
<p><span>Set back from the main centre of Levi, these apartments enjoy a quiet location whilst being close to all of the resort amenities including the supermarket, bars and restaurants in the centre of resort. The ski slopes and ski lifts are around four minutes from the apartments, so you can easily get onto the well groomed slopes each day. If you are taking part in one of our <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">optional extras</a> the meeting point is </span>close-by - enjoy whizzing through the snowy landscapes on snowmobiles or enjoy a serene sleigh ride through the wooded areas.</p>]]></description>
