  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studio apartments </strong>are about 26m² and sleep up to two adults and one child. These renovated semi-detached apartments are set over one level and have an open-plan kitchen and living area with a fireplace (firewood included) and a sofa-bed, and a sleeping alcove with a double bed. </p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> are about 46m² and sleep up to four adults and one child. These apartments are part of a terrace of apartments, and are set over one level. There is an open-plan kitchen/living area with a fireplace (firewood included), and two twin bedrooms with single beds. In one of the bedrooms there is a third bed suitable for a child above the twin beds that can be reached by steps. </p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments</strong> are about 63m² and sleep up to six adults and one child. These apartments are part of a terrace of apartments and are set over two levels. Downstairs there is a lounge area, kitchen and one twin bedroom. Upstairs has two twin bedrooms, one with a third bed. Please note that the upper level has a sloping roof. These apartments do not have a fire place. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment Facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Flat-screen TV,</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Full kitchen consisting of an oven, fridge, microwave, coffee-maker, toaster, dishwasher, washing machine (excludes Studio apartments 19 &amp; 20) </li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made up on arrival</li>
<li>Final clean included (bins to be emptied on departure)</li>
<li>Cots are free of charge and available on request at the time of booking (subject to availability)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
